          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2019-09-16T20:25:13Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Defense (DOD) to establish family and medical leave banks for DOD employees.</p> <p>It requires the forfeited annual leave (i.e., the lost &quot;use it or lose it&quot; annual leave) of an employee to be credited to a family and medical leave bank for use by an eligible employee who experiences a personal or family medical emergency and has exhausted his or her available paid leave.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2019-04-10T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
